                                <div class="mattress_buying_guide_list_item">
                                    <span class="mattress_buying_guide_desktop_list-title">ADJUSTABLE BASE</span>
                                    <span class="mattress_buying_guide_desktop_list-description">Adjustable bases allow for unlimited ergonomic positions to support the natural curvature of the spine and ensure the ultimate comfort.</span>
