                                <div class="mattress_buying_guide_list_item">
                                    <span class="mattress_buying_guide_desktop_list-title">COOLING</span>
                                    <span class="mattress_buying_guide_desktop_list-description">An advanced technology wicks away body heat to provide temperature-controlled, restful and restorative sleep.</span>
