                        <section id="mattress_buying_guide_desktop_well_made_bed" class="desktop_section" style="display: none;">
                            <div class="mattress_buying_guide-row">
                                <div class="mattress_buying_guide-col mbg-col-left well_made_bed_text_left">
                                    <span class="mattress_buying_guide_h1" id="mattress_buying_guide_h1-well_made_bed">A WELL-MADE BED</span>
                                    <div class="mattress_buying_guide_p p-well_made_bed"><span class="serif_font">&#x25AE;</span> CONSTRUCTION</div>
                                    <span class="well_made_bed-title">INNERSPRING</span>
                                    <span class="mattress_buying_guide_p">Combines supportive coils with cushioned upholstery. Encased (or pocketed) coils conform to the body and reduce motion transfer while other types of coils are less elastic, providing extra support.</span>
                                    <span class="well_made_bed-title">LATEX</span>
                                    <span class="mattress_buying_guide_p">These hypoallergenic mattresses boast a long lifespan and good support while lightly conforming to the body&rsquo;s shape for significant pressure relief. And because they&rsquo;re breathable, they also offer excellent airflow to help regulate body temperature.</span>
                                    <span class="well_made_bed-title">MEMORY FOAM</span>
                                    <span class="mattress_buying_guide_p">Foam mattresses mold to your body, offering support while relieving pressure. Memory foam also reduces motion transfer, so you&rsquo;re less likely to be disturbed by movement on the other side of the bed.</span>
                                    <span class="well_made_bed-title">PILLOW TOP</span>
                                    <span class="mattress_buying_guide_p">Constructed using extra layers of upholstery that are separately quilted and sewn to the top of a mattress for added cushioning.</span>
                                    <span class="well_made_bed-title">HYBRID</span>
                                    <span class="mattress_buying_guide_p">Blending the comfort of memory foam or latex with the support.</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mattress_buying_guide-col mbg-col-right">
                                    <img src="/fashion/images/projects/fashion-tips/mattress-buying-guide/mattress_buying_guide_desktop-well_made_bed01.jpg">
                                </div>
                                <div class="mattress_buying_guide_clear"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mattress_buying_guide-row">
                                <div class="mattress_buying_guide-col mbg-col-left">
                                    <img src="/fashion/images/projects/fashion-tips/mattress-buying-guide/mattress_buying_guide_desktop-well_made_bed02.jpg">
                                </div>
                                <div class="mattress_buying_guide-col well_made_bed_text_right">
                                    <div class="mattress_buying_guide_p p-well_made_bed mbg_reset_margin_top"><span class="serif_font">&#x25AE;</span> COMFORT LEVEL</div>
                                    <span class="well_made_bed_libre_font">Support has to do with <i>your body</i>, not the mattress.</span>
                                    <span class="mattress_buying_guide_p">A comfortable mattress is one that relieves pressure points for you. What&rsquo;s right varies significantly from person to person. The perfect mattress offers the same natural curve your back has when you&rsquo;re standing.</span>
                                    <span class="well_made_bed-title">FIRM</span>
                                    <span class="mattress_buying_guide_p">A sturdy top with little to no give.</span>
                                    <span class="well_made_bed-title">MEDIUM FIRM</span>
                                    <span class="mattress_buying_guide_p">A firm top with some give.</span>
                                    <span class="well_made_bed-title">MEDIUM PLUSH</span>
                                    <span class="mattress_buying_guide_p">Noticeable give, medium soft.</span>
                                    <span class="well_made_bed-title">PLUSH</span>
                                    <span class="mattress_buying_guide_p">Soft with significant give.</span>
                                    <div class="well_made_bed_comfort_level_bottom_text">
                                        <span class="comfort_level_black_circle">Tip</span>
                                        <span class="well_made_bed_libre_bottom">To check your mattress, lie down and slide your hand under the small of your back. If it passes through too easily, your mattress may be too firm.</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mattress_buying_guide_clear"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div id="well_made_bed_size_section">
                                <img src="/fashion/images/projects/fashion-tips/mattress-buying-guide/mattress_buying_guide_desktop-well_made_bed-size.jpg">
                            </div>
                            <div class="mattress_buying_guide-row">
                                <div class="mattress_buying_guide-col mbg-col-left well_made_bed_text_left">
                                    <div class="mattress_buying_guide_p p-well_made_bed mbg_reset_margin_top"><span class="serif_font">&#x25AE;</span> FOUNDATION</div>
                                    <span class="well_made_bed_libre_font">Designed to provide sturdy, stable support for your mattress, a box spring will also absorb shock, reduce wear and make it easier to get in and out of bed.</span>
                                    <span class="well_made_bed_libre_font">Increasingly, more foundations are being created from wood alone, a style that provides excellent support for modern memory foam and latex mattresses.</span>
                                    <span class="well_made_bed-title">STANDARD BOX-SPRING</span>
                                    <span class="mattress_buying_guide_p">The most common foundation. Consists of tight, supportive springs in a wood frame. 9&rdquo; high.</span>
                                    <span class="well_made_bed-title">LOW-PROFILE BOX-SPRING</span>
                                    <span class="mattress_buying_guide_p">Usually 5&rdquo; in height, these are ideal for high frames or thick mattresses to reduce overall height.</span>
                                    <span class="well_made_bed-title">SPLIT BOX-SPRING</span>
                                    <span class="mattress_buying_guide_p">Two separate box springs. This method is used on all king and California king beds to more easily transport the box springs.</span>
                                    <span class="well_made_bed-title">ADJUSTABLE BASE</span>
                                    <span class="mattress_buying_guide_p">With a host of customizable options, these bases allow you to fine-tune your support.</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mattress_buying_guide-col mbg-col-right">
                                    <img src="/fashion/images/projects/fashion-tips/mattress-buying-guide/mattress_buying_guide_desktop-well_made_bed03.jpg">
